<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB08194</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT MANDATING THE DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH TO ESTABLISH A RESEARCH CENTER ON OBESITY PREVENTION</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to protect Filipinos from the harmful effect of obesity by establishing research center on obesity prevention and information propaganda to help the public understand the nature of this condition.

Enumerates several conditions or diseases that accompanies an overweight and obese person.
